Text:
Thank you for the pictures of some very beautiful women.

Now could we have their names in Roman alphabet rather than Cyrillic?

Thanks.

Thanks!

For those who want translation to Roman, Google translate helped nicely here:

Биляна Йотовска = Biljana Yotovska
Златка Димитрова = Zlatka Dimitrova
Кристина Димитрова = Kristina Dimitrova
Марина Маринова = Marina Marinova
Полина Котева = Polina Koteva
Силвия Димитрова-Бахати = Silvia Dimitrova-Bahaty
